Located near [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]], the '''Sea of Veruna''' was a quadrant of dead space in the [[Naboo system/Legends|Naboo system]], usually safe for travel and [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] jumps. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] sought to clamp down on unauthorized travel in the region.

